{"tid":1358021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[一定要齊防具] 721黑警狂放催淚彈 開槍既原因","createTime":"2019-07-24T00:22:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T02:21:34.000Z","uid":105976,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"54a8fe5533f9640948694725fd279bebe06ddfa7","tid":1358021,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:22:06.000Z","msg":"前排既人裝備比以前齊全好多<br />\n地盤頭盔+單車盔 + 豬嘴 +泳鏡護目鏡<br />\n戴得好冇漏氣就做到100%防催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n豬嘴點配請睇:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1357161/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1357161/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n警方果晚清場係清得極慢   首先因為沙田一役 好明顯黑警要保持距離唔敢埋身<br />\n二黎d街真係好撚窄<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">三黎. 好多人裝備齊全可以係前線100%擋催淚彈</span></strong><br />\n以致佢地清場行動更加低效率<br />\n<br />\n所以結論係<br />\n齊防具  d人企定定係到乜都唔做 &gt;黑警放催淚彈&gt; 再放多d&gt; 無效  開槍<br />\n<br />\n簡單d就係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">企定定乜都唔做 &gt;  開槍  </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要做好d文宣追究佢無啦啦開槍<br />\n然後如果和理非都有晒防具 企定定乜都唔做 黑警放催淚又冇效<br />\n唔通佢又直接橡膠彈射你?"},{"pid":"08c3f792b5c5cf74e4dc751008db03b04674c635","tid":1358021,"uid":105976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:26:18.000Z","msg":"一定要齊防具!!!<br />\n<br />\n豬嘴+氣密泳鏡<br />\n<br />\n泳鏡要岩size 盡量冇罅<br />\n仲係有罅就用熱融膠槍封住佢<br />\n書局/五金鋪都有  50~100蚊  記得要買埋幾條膠<br />\n<a href=\"https://a.ecimg.tw/items/DEAC5GA64813822/i010001_1462919242.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ecimg.tw%2Fitems%2FDEAC5GA64813822%2Fi010001_1462919242.jpg&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1bHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=9c6ba484\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://a.ecimg.tw/items/DEAC5GA64813822/i010001_1462919242.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"632d302a6fb9cb554bd3fe2c6ce9bd54f4461f47","tid":1358021,"uid":4496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:28:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a772ed03246a99a448f0b563eaa7db1689689217","tid":1358021,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T0